{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:07:12.047969+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: ab968d1bccce03314b795f6e7ecc3c2608383762)", "id": "lc_635b7c69-7242-46a3-950b-8a381d024766"}, {"type": "text", "text": "from os import environ\n\nfrom passlib.context import CryptContext\n\n\nclass Settings:\n    APP_TITLE = \"App name\"\n    ALLOWED_HOST = environ.get(\"ALLOWED_HOST\")\n    SECRET_KEY = environ.get(\"SECRET_KEY\")\n    DEBUG = bool(environ.get(\"DEBUG\"))\n    ALLOWED_PORT = int(environ.get(\"PORT\"))\n    DB_USER = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_USER\")\n    DB_PASSWORD = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_PASSWORD\")\n    DB_DB = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_DB\")\n    DB_PORT = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_PORT\")\n    DB_HOST = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_HOST\")\n    DB_URL = (\n        f\"postgresql+psycopg2://{DB_USER}:{DB_PASSWORD}@{DB_HOST}:{DB_PORT}/{DB_DB}\"\n    )\n    TEST_DB = environ.get(\"POSTGRES_TEST_DB\")\n    TEST_DB_URL = (\n        f\"postgresql+psycopg2://{DB_USER}:{DB_PASSWORD}@{DB_HOST}:{DB_PORT}/{TEST_DB}\"\n    )\n    ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRY_TIME = 60 * 30\n    REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRY_TIME = 60 * 24 * 365\n    PASSWORD_HASHER = CryptContext(schemes=[\"bcrypt\"], deprecated=\"auto\")\n    JWT_ALGORITHM = \"HS256\"\n    REDIS_HOST = environ.get(\"REDIS_HOST\", \"localhost\")\n    REDIS_PORT = environ.get(\"REDIS_PORT\", \"6379\")\n    PAGE_SIZE = 50\n\n\nsettings = Settings()", "id": "lc_a9e4d63e-7ef8-4386-a86d-5a6121444adb"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "a9d82f4f-b827-46de-bd0b-cb6b8943edff", "tool_call_id": "call_00_LbSUR5QyXGLd4ATFQIWo1756", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:07:23.720906+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Findings: Main Python Dependency & Service Stack\n\nBased on my analysis of the repository, here is the complete breakdown:\n\n---\n\n### **Main Python Dependency: FastAPI**\nThe core framework is **FastAPI** (with `[all]` extras), which bundles Uvicorn (ASGI server), Pydantic, Starlette, and other standard FastAPI tooling.\n\n---\n\n### **Database Stack**\n| Component | Library | Purpose |\n|-----------|---------|---------|\n| **Database** | **PostgreSQL** | Primary relational database (via `postgres` Docker image) |\n| ORM | **SQLAlchemy** (Core + ORM) | Database modeling, metadata, sessions |\n| Async DB | **databases** (with `[postgresql]` extras) | Async database queries |\n| Driver (sync) | **psycopg2** | PostgreSQL adapter for SQLAlchemy |\n| Driver (async) | **asyncpg** | Async PostgreSQL driver |\n| Utilities | **sqlalchemy-utils** | Helpers like `database_exists`, `create_database` |\n| Migrations | **Alembic** | Schema migration tool (configured via `alembic.ini`) |\n\n---\n\n### **Auth-Related Libraries**\n| Library | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| **python-jose** (with `[cryptography]` extras) | JWT encoding/decoding (`jose.jwt`) |\n| **passlib** (with `[bcrypt]` extras) | Password hashing via `CryptContext` with bcrypt scheme |\n| **python-multipart** | Required for OAuth2 form-data parsing |\n| `fastapi.security.OAuth2PasswordBearer` | OAuth2 password flow for OpenAPI/Swagger integration |\n\nJWT algorithm used: **HS256**. Token types: access tokens (30 min expiry) and refresh tokens (365 day expiry).\n\n---\n\n### **Redis Support**\n- **aioredis** — async Redis client library\n- Redis is configured as a **docker-compose service** (`redis:alpine` image) and wired via `REDIS_HOST`/`REDIS_PORT` environment variables.\n\n---\n\n### **Service Stack (docker-compose.yml)**\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  web (FastAPI)         :11000        │\n│  postgres (PostgreSQL) :5432         │\n│  redis (Redis:alpine)  :6379         │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n### **Complete Dependency List (Pipfile)**\n| Package | Extras |\n|---------|--------|\n| `fastapi` | `[all]` |\n| `alembic` | — |\n| `psycopg2` | — |\n| `databases` | `[postgresql]` |\n| `asyncpg` | — |\n| `python-jose` | `[cryptography]` |\n| `passlib` | `[bcrypt]` |\n| `python-multipart` | — |\n| `pytest` | — |\n| `sqlalchemy-utils` | — |\n| `aioredis` | — |\n\n**Python version**: 3.9 (specified in Pipfile `[requires]`)", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1067, "prompt_tokens": 10133, "total_tokens": 11200, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 375, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 9728}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 9728, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 405}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "1d3eb977-3999-4c57-ad73-fcee311c35ad", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3b2-4db0-7532-948d-3f22dcea2137-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10133, "output_tokens": 1067, "total_tokens": 11200, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 9728}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 375}}}}]}}}
